Installation:
        If you want to install this extension, follow these spteps:
                * First, download the extension from http://code.google.com/p/pieceofcode-dr/downloads/list. This will give you a tar.gz file.
                * Second, extract the tar.gz file inside you mediawiki extensions directory. This will create a folder called PieceOfCode-dr.
                * Third, add this line at the end of you LocalSettings.php file:
                        require_once("extensions/PieceOfCode-dr/PieceOfCode-dr.php");
		  And a configuration like this one:
			$wgPieceOfCodeSVNConnections['MyProyect'] = array(
				'url'		=> 'https://myproyect.googlecode.com',
				'username'	=> 'myusername',
				'password'	=> 'mypassword',
			);

                * Then, enjoy!.

Links:
        * MediaWiki Extensions: http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:PieceOfCode
        * GoogleCode Proyect Site: http://code.google.com/p/pieceofcode-dr/
        * GoogleCode Issues trak: http://code.google.com/p/pieceofcode-dr/issues
